title: #92Noon! 9am Hour 2/21 - Nordo in for PA! Pat Micheletti
description: –Nordo fills in for PA who’s in Colorado, Pat Micheletti joins the show to talk all things Wild after their dominant showing last night in Edmonton, and Nordo discusses his enjoyment of the NFL Combine.
